[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0884","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1029","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9138,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10822}}","description":"SSH 服务端 sshd2 在 2.0.12 之前版本存在认证日志缺陷。该服务在远程连接于达到最大登录尝试次数之前被关闭时，未能正确记录此次登录尝试。由于失败尝试未被写入审计日志，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过建立连接、尝试少量密码后主动断开并重连的方式，对目标账户进行密码暴力破解，同时规避入侵检测与审计追踪。该漏洞影响所有早于 2.0.12 的 sshd2 版本，攻击仅需网络可达目标 SSH 服务且无需合法凭据，利用门槛低，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1029"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.427","remediation":"升级 SSH2 服务端至 2.0.12 或更高版本以修复审计日志绕过问题。若暂无法升级，可在 sshd 配置中降低 PasswordAuthentication 最大尝试次数（MaxAuthTries）、启用公钥认证并禁用密码登录，同时部署 fail2ban 对失败登录进行封禁，并结合防火墙限制 SSH 端口来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004280&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/277","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2193","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1029","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1029.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/277/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-223.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7c795f8b-9ad3-4a47-b7c5-c836dcd4935e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1368","title":"Computer Associates InoculateIT MS Exchange Server 选项病毒绕过检测漏洞","description":"InoculateIT 4.53 及可能其他版本的 MS Exchange Server 防病毒选项仅扫描 Microsoft Exchange 服务器的收件箱文件夹树，当用户邮件规则将邮件移动到其他邮箱时，病毒可绕过检测。攻击者利用此设计缺陷，通过将含病毒邮件移出收件箱即可逃避扫描，导致系统被感染。该漏洞影响 InoculateIT 4.53 及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1368"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.480","remediation":"升级 InoculateIT 至 4.53 以上版本，确保 AV 选项配置为扫描所有 Exchange 邮箱文件夹而非仅收件箱。如厂商已停止支持，建议迁移至其他支持全邮箱扫描的防病毒方案（如 Microsoft Defender for Office 365），并禁用自动移动邮件的用户规则作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92652152723629&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=97439568517355&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgqh-3fh5-37xc/GHSA-qgqh-3fh5-37xc.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000635.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9186387f-2fa8-40f8-814b-8ce0daf4dc95.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0017","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0229","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IIS 目录遍历拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在路径遍历拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含特殊构造的 `..\\..` 序列的 HTTP 请求触发目录遍历，导致服务器资源耗尽或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上的 Microsoft IIS 服务，利用方式简单，危害性较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0229"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.530","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（含 IIS 5.0+），或在 Windows NT 4.0 上安装 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 及 MS98-004 安全补丁。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用未使用的虚拟目录并移除可执行权限以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0229.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_crash.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2218/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0229.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0507","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0776","title":"Alibaba HTTP 服务器 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Alibaba HTTP 服务器存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞。该服务器未能正确过滤 HTTP 请求中的 ../（点点）路径序列，导致远程攻击者可在未认证的情况下，通过构造包含点号序列的特制 HTTP 请求读取 Web 根目录之外的任意文件。受影响范围为运行 Alibaba HTTP 服务器的系统，攻击条件仅需攻击者能与目标服务器建立普通 HTTP 连接。利用方式通常为在 GET 请求的路径中拼接 ../../../../etc/passwd 等序列，从而获取系统口令文件、配置文件或源代码等敏感信息，造成信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0776"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-12","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"该 Alibaba HTTP 服务器已停止维护，建议立即停用并迁移至受支持的主流 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx）。迁移前可在前端部署反向代理或 WAF，配置规则拦截请求路径中包含 ../ 或编码形式的目录遍历序列作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0776","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0776.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1157","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1157.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1520","title":"Microsoft Site Server Commerce Edition 3.0 alpha AdSamples 目录敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server Commerce Edition 3.0 alpha 的 Ad Server Sample 目录（AdSamples）存在配置错误，导致攻击者可直接访问并下载 SITE.CSC 文件，该文件包含敏感的 SQL 数据库连接信息（如服务器地址、数据库名、用户名、密码等）。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问 AdSamples 目录下的 SITE.CSC 文件获取数据库敏感信息，进而可能进一步攻击数据库服务器。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server Commerce Edition 3.0 alpha 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），攻击者只需构造针对 AdSamples 目录的 HTTP 请求即可无需认证获取敏感配置文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1520"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-18T00:00:00.000","remediation":"删除或限制对 AdSamples 目录下 SITE.CSC 文件的 Web 访问权限（如通过 IIS 移除该目录的匿名读取权限或设置 NTFS ACL），并修改其中暴露的 SQL 数据库账户密码，升级至已修复该配置问题的后续版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92647407227303&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/256","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2270","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19208"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1157.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1157.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1157.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0608","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0754","title":"INN inndstart 权限提升漏洞","description":"INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器的 inndstart 程序存在权限提升漏洞。该程序在启动时会信任并读取由环境变量 INNCONF 所指定的配置文件路径，本地已登录的普通用户可通过在运行 inndstart 前自行设置 INNCONF 环境变量，将其指向攻击者可控的恶意配置文件，从而诱导以特权（如 news 用户或 root）身份运行的 inndstart 加载该配置并执行其中的危险指令或参数，最终实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响使用存在缺陷版本 INN 软件且允许本地用户执行 inndstart 的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击前提是攻击者需具备目标系统的本地账户访问权限且系统未对 INNCONF 环境变量做安全过滤。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0754"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.240","remediation":"建议升级 INN (InterNetNews) 至 2.2.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了 inndstart 的 INNCONF 环境变量权限提升漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可通过在用户登录脚本或 /etc/profile 中取消设置 INNCONF 环境变量（unset INNCONF），并限制普通用户对 inndstart 的执行权限（chmod 750 /usr/local/news/bin/inndstart）作为临时缓解措施。建议参考 ISC 官方安全公告升级至 INN 2.6.0 或更新版本彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/corp/support/errata/inn99_05_22.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/255","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0754.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0754","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0754.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-c5pf-965c-g6g8/GHSA-c5pf-965c-g6g8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/255/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0514","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0785","title":"ISC INN inndstart 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ISC INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器软件中的 inndstart 程序存在权限管理缺陷，由于未对 inn.conf 配置文件中的 \"pathrun\" 参数进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的 pathrun 路径参数，使 inndstart 以 root 权限执行任意程序，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 ISC INN 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或严格限制 inn.conf 文件的写入权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0785"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.197","remediation":"升级 ISC INN 至 2.2.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 inndstart 对 pathrun 参数的不安全处理。如无法升级，确保 inn.conf 中 pathrun 指向受保护目录（如 /usr/local/news/bin），且该目录仅允许 root 用户写入，同时移除 inndstart 的 setuid root 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/254"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0514.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0501","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0773","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 lpset 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 lpset 命令在处理命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于程序未对用户输入的打印机名称等参数进行长度校验，本地攻击者可通过构造超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而将普通用户权限提升至 root。该漏洞属于本地利用，攻击者可借助 setuid 位安装的 lpset 程序完成权限提升，影响运行 Solaris 7 且未打补丁的主机。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0773"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 Solaris 补丁版本（建议安装 Sun 补丁簇 107115-xx 或更高版本，使用 patchadd 命令安装）。在无法立即打补丁前，可临时移除 /usr/bin/lpset 的 setuid 权限（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpset），并限制其仅由 lp 系统用户访问，以消除本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.netspace.org/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind9905B&L=bugtraq&P=R2017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19206","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0773.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0568","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0806","title":"Sun Solaris dtprintinfo 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中的 dtprintinfo 打印信息管理程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序通常以 setuid root 权限运行，本地攻击者可通过向程序传入超长参数或环境变量触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而将本地普通用户权限提升至 root 权限，完全控制受影响系统。攻击条件为攻击者已获得本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0806"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-10","updated":"1999-05-10","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方针对 dtprintinfo 缓冲区溢出发布的安全补丁；在补丁未部署前，可移除 dtprintinfo 程序的 setuid 位以降低本地提权风险，并严格限制本地用户账户的分配。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0806"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1189","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1189.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1566","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10368,\"inputTokens\":442,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10827}}","description":"iParty Conferencing Server 1.2 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过连接默认端口 6004 并发送重复的扩展字符触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃并造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 iParty 会议服务器的所有受影响版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络层面可达目标端口即可实施。利用方式为向服务发送特制的畸形数据包，导致缓冲区溢出使服务进程异常终止，从而使合法用户无法使用会议服务。CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中等危害级别。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1566"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.843","remediation":"建议立即升级 iParty Conferencing Server 至 1.3 或更高版本以修复默认端口 6004 上的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或边界网关上通过 ACL 规则阻断对 TCP 6004 端口的外部访问，并仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址连接，作为临时缓解措施。同时建议在网络边界部署入侵检测规则，拦截向该端口发送大量扩展字符的异常连接请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13600","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22250","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1566.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1566","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1566.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1566.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-499h-7q88-4fxx/GHSA-499h-7q88-4fxx.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/iParty.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1566.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000630.txt","https://github.com/c2siorg/bug-connector/blob/68c960cc01a4f61c238e8a780d2247db700d4a9b/Datasets/Mapped_CVE_file.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1189.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0357","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0357.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0739","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server codebrws.asp 示例文件任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server 中的 codebrws.asp 示例文件存在安全漏洞，该文件原本用于展示代码浏览功能，但由于缺乏适当的访问控制和路径过滤，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意请求利用该文件读取服务器上的任意文件，包括系统敏感配置文件、用户凭据等。攻击者无需任何身份认证即可发起攻击，只需知道或猜测目标文件路径即可获取服务器上的敏感数据。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS 和 Site Server，建议删除或限制访问该示例文件，并及时升级到安全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0739"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.393","remediation":"立即删除或禁用 IIS/Site Server 中的 codebrws.asp 示例文件，安装微软安全公告 MS99-013 提供的补丁程序。由于 IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0 已停止支持，强烈建议升级至现代版本 IIS 10（Windows Server 2016/2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：通过 IIS 管理器移除所有示例应用程序目录，配置 NTFS 权限限制 web 目录的匿名访问，并使用 Web 服务器防火墙规则阻止对 /codebrws.asp 路径的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0739.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0739","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0739.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0739.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/iis_codebrws.nasl","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0739.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/4edc9938788d3f7fc2435789a001f306b27788b7/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/chihsuan/search-engine/blob/9dcdd3e644469883f53565740f0ba8ff617c5120/Data/E99D88C1-C798-40D7-BB8C-47E6405B9469.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0739.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0357.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0357.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0357.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0356","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0738","title":"Microsoft IIS 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Services（IIS）及 Site Server 中的 code.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程未经身份认证的攻击者可利用该示例文件，通过构造特殊 HTTP 请求读取目标服务器上的任意文件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响包含该示例文件的 IIS 及 Site Server 版本，攻击者无需登录凭据即可在未授权情况下访问服务器文件系统中的机密数据。该漏洞属于信息泄露类安全风险，攻击者可能借此获取配置文件、数据库凭证或其他敏感信息，为后续进一步攻击提供条件。Microsoft 建议管理员删除或限制该示例文件的访问权限以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0738"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.270","remediation":"立即从 IIS 和 Site Server 的 Web 根目录（如 \\inetpub\\wwwroot 及 \\Program Files\\Microsoft Site Server）中删除 code.asp 等示例脚本文件；安装微软对应安全补丁（Windows NT 4.0 SP4 / IIS 4.0 累积更新），并将 Site Server 升级至已修正该问题的版本；在无法立即升级时，使用 IIS 的“执行权限”设为“无”来禁用脚本目录执行，并通过 URLScan 拒绝包含 ../ 的路径遍历请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0738","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0738.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-92vg-86x4-j5qj/GHSA-92vg-86x4-j5qj.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/4edc9938788d3f7fc2435789a001f306b27788b7/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88076/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0355","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0737","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 附带的 viewcode.asp 示例脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向该脚本发送包含目标文件路径的特制 HTTP 请求，读取服务器文件系统中的任意文件内容，包括配置文件、源代码及敏感数据。该漏洞影响安装了上述示例脚本且未删除或未打补丁的 IIS 4.0 与 Site Server 版本，攻击者仅需目标服务器开放 Web 服务即可利用，无需任何凭据。Microsoft 已在 MS99-013 安全公告中发布补丁，建议删除 viewcode.asp 等示例脚本或升级至修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0737"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.140","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 4.0 安装目录下 /scripts/showcode.asp、viewcode.asp 等示例脚本文件（默认位于 C:\\WINNT\\System32\\inetsrv\\scripts\\），并升级到 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 3 或更高版本；无法立即升级时，应在 IIS 管理器中移除示例站点并配置 NTFS 权限禁止匿名用户读取敏感目录作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0737.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0737","https://github.com/GuangrenYu/WangYi/blob/db7e4b8b6d2f1d5bfd5908a02b4b5fcac6b3880d/poc_kb/custom/1999/CVE-1999-0737.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/82035e540ee415f78310ba979a19dffd78d3cfa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0737.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrf7-29w2-32h3/GHSA-mrf7-29w2-32h3.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0737.yaml","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/iis_viewcode.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0737.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0352","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0736","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10794,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中的 showcode.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造特制请求访问该文件，进而读取目标服务器上的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0 版本，攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用此漏洞窃取敏感信息。showcode.asp 作为 IIS 和 Site Server 自带的演示脚本，未对文件路径进行充分限制，允许攻击者通过参数指定服务器上的任意文件路径进行读取，导致信息泄露风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0736"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.020","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-013 发布的补丁以修复该漏洞。受影响版本为 IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0，应下载并安装对应的安全更新。如无法立即安装补丁，可删除或禁用服务器上的 showcode.asp、viewcode.asp、code.asp、codebrws.asp 等示例文件查看工具，因为这些文件仅用于演示目的，不应在生产服务器上运行。同时通过 NTFS 权限配置限制对这些文件的访问，或在 IIS 中移除相关虚拟目录映射，以阻止远程用户通过 Web 请求读取服务器上的敏感文件。此外，在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务器端口的外部访问，并确保 Web 根目录之外的敏感文件系统文件不具有 Web 用户读取权限，作为额外缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A932","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19129","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0736.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0736.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0736","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/82035e540ee415f78310ba979a19dffd78d3cfa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0736.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0736.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mjqv-8fmv-523x/GHSA-mjqv-8fmv-523x.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0736.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/ShowCode.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0736.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0352.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0352.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0316","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0316.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0717","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 病毒警告机制禁用漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 的病毒警告机制存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可通过构造特制的 Excel 文件，在用户打开该文件时绕过内置的病毒警告提示，从而在用户不知情的情况下执行恶意宏代码。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 版本，攻击者需诱使用户打开恶意文件，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0717"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.573","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Office 2000 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 Excel 中的宏自动执行功能，并在打开来自互联网的 Excel 文件前启用病毒警告机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231304","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-014","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0717.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0717.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0717","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0717.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0717.json","https://github.com/opencve/openc